      <title>移民问题加剧 瑞士人口激增 创 1960 年代以来新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/swiss-population-jumps-most-since-1960s-amid-immigration-tension</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士人口增幅达到半个多世纪以来的最高水平，这进一步加剧了有关该国是否应该向移民敞开大门的争论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/swiss-population-jumps-most-since-1960s-amid-immigration-tension</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 14:48:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克时代严厉打击导致英国卫生工作者签证数量急剧下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/sunak-era-crackdown-causes-sharp-fall-in-uk-health-worker-visas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据内政部的最新数据，英国前首相里希·苏纳克（Rishi Sunak）领导的保守党政府采取的打击措施，导致发放给海外卫生工作者的签证数量急剧下降，这是新工党政府在移民问题上喜忧参半的遗产之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/sunak-era-crackdown-causes-sharp-fall-in-uk-health-worker-visas</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 13:40:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>他信提出拯救泰国摆脱债务陷阱的策略</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/thaksin-pitches-strategy-to-rescue-thailand-from-debt-trap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国前总理他信·西那瓦表示，泰国需要紧急解决高额家庭和公共债务问题，并集中精力制定政策，推动泰国经济增速与一些东南亚邻国相媲美。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/thaksin-pitches-strategy-to-rescue-thailand-from-debt-trap</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 12:56:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国计划简化高收入者解雇金融</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/germany-eyes-loosening-job-protections-for-finance-high-earners</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为了与法国和英国竞争吸引顶尖银行家，德国政府已制定计划，让解雇金融行业高收入者变得更加容易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/germany-eyes-loosening-job-protections-for-finance-high-earners</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 12:49:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯军队不顾库尔斯克号入侵乌克兰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/russian-army-presses-on-in-ukraine-despite-kursk-incursion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯在奋力击退基辅军队跨境入侵其领土的同时，仍在推进对乌克兰东部的攻势。]]></description>
