    <item>
      <title>土耳其希望通过罕见部长级会议重启与欧盟的关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/turkey-eu-ties-foreign-minister-hakan-fidan-to-visit-brussels</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其外交部长哈坎·菲丹将于 8 月 29 日与欧盟外交部长举行非正式会谈，这是欧盟五年来的首次，欧盟正致力于改善与土耳其的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/turkey-eu-ties-foreign-minister-hakan-fidan-to-visit-brussels</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 12:14:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
